## Description
The **On-demand program&nbsp;**resource&nbsp;allows to use a custom program in an on-demand workflow to process data using Java.

> Note

For more information, see: [How to Create a Java Program for an On-Demand Workflow](https://code.doxee.com/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=123860359).

## Additional creation parameters
None.

## Resource editor
None.

## Release parameters
![](data:image/png;base64,)

Field

Description

**Platform**

Select the program's platform:

- **Java**

- **Python**

**File**

Click&nbsp;**Upload** to select&nbsp;the file containing the program.

> Important

Java programs must be in JAR format, Python programs must be in ZIP format.

**Summary**

Brief description of the release
